-|-------|----------------|\n| June | S. 35° 31' W 36°       |                          |                                           |                                          |         |     |                                          |         |     |          |       | W by N, SW |\n|      | 16° 24' 23\"            | 37° 56'                  |                                           |                                          |         |     |                                          |         |     |          |       | SE, NW |\n|      | 17° 34' 44\"            | 49° 7'                   |                                           |                                          |         |     |                                          |         |     |          |       | NW, SE by S |\n|      | 18° 33' 48\"            | 42° 3'                   |                                           |                                          |         |     |                                          |         |     |          |       | E by S |\n|      | 19° 34' 48\"            | 42° 24'                  |                                           |                                          |         |     |                                          |         |     |          |       | NE |\n|      | 20° 34' 54\"            | 45° 17'                  |                                           |                                          |         |     |                                          |         |     |          |       | N |\n|      | 21° 35' 7\"             | 48° 40'                  |                                           |                                          |         |     |                                          |         |     |          |       | WNW |\n|      | 22° 34' 34\"            | 51° 35'                  |                                           |                                          |         |     |                                        